            . I am clerk to the prosecutors'. The prisoner was to account to me daily for what he received; he has never accounted for 2l. 8s. received from Cockin on the 26th of August - I believe this receipt of the 25th of September to be his writing; he never brought this 1l. 7s. to account; nor the 1l. 17s. 6d. from Lart - I believe this receipt to be his hand-writing.</p>
